 ```
  
  ---
  
  ## FILE 22 — `.gitignore`
  ```
  node_modules
  dist
  dist-ssr
  .env
  .env.local
  .env.*.local
  *.log
  .DS_Store
  .vscode/
  .idea/
  ```
  
  ---
  
  ## 🗄️ How to Connect Supabase
  ```
  1. Go to supabase.com → create a free account → New Project
  2. Go to SQL Editor → New Query
  3. Paste supabase_schema.sql → click Run
  4. Go to Settings → API
  5. Copy Project URL + anon key into your .env file